---
title: Pineapple Upside Down Cake with Coconut Caramel & Toasted Coconut | Serves 8+
description: Do you remember this retro classic? We may have taken a few liberties with the original, like adding a coconut caramel sauce.
This cake will be sure to impress when you flip it upside to reveal the sticky caramel pineapple layer!
